Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you take your friends for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Anger Explosion!\NKuro vs. Luffy, How it Ends!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Out of the Back Attack does\Nhave lots of unnecessary movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything so far has been playtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get the special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to let you taste plenty\Nof fear, then slowly cook you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the Back Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try your foot technique now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now your plan of three\Nyears is a complete failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He caught Captain Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if he wins, that means\Nwe won't get killed, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're one\Nstep too late, Haramaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That branch was in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'im, Rubber Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick Captain Kuro's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have no right to cheer me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this, hypnotist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain!\N--Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack: Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--My plan will not be disrupted!\N--...Bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He beat him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He beat Captain Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even the navy was a match\Nfor Kuro, Man of a Thousand Plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he really beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never lose to a pirate who ditches\Nhis name and runs from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only time a pirate should\Nabandon his name is when he dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy?! Yeah, I never\Nheard that name before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember my name for\Nthe rest of your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who's gonna\Nbe King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him and leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never come here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry!\N--Raise the anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect even you to collapse\Nafter all you just went through...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you mad about earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate them. They're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:07:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how friends should act.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?\NOf course it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates aren't the lovely things\Nyou make them out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say Captain Kuro's\Nmore standard than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want some meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you keep everything that's\Njust happened here a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! A secret?! How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! After we just fought\Nfor the village's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone'll change their\Nopinion of you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be the village hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah! Yeah!\N--Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san. You need to clear up\Neveryone's misunderstanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misunderstanding? I was only\Ncalled an exaggerator, like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to scare everyone\Nwith something that's already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from things like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no pirates will show up to attack\Na remote village like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to pretend\Nthat nothing ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't force you to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can do it! If it's for\Nthe best of the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too! I'll never say a word, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be hard for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Usopp-kun this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It throws everything off for some\Nreason... I can't get motivated...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the liar guy not coming today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn exaggeration-spewing kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think maybe I was\Ntoo harsh yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be back to his old tricks\Ncome tomorrow! I'm sure of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have been able to protect\Nthe village without you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't done anything,\NI would've done nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that?\NI got me some treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This incident has helped me\Nfinally come to a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Usopp! What did you\Nwant to talk to us about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys fought well against\Nthose Black Cat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As captain, I feel very proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're too kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're nothing compared to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're embarrassing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you really did great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were scared to death,\Nbut you managed to keep Kaya safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We overcame our biggest and\Ngreatest battle since we formed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Usopp Pirates five years ago,\Nwhen you guys were just four!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes!\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I know this is sudden, but I've\Ndecided to set out to sea by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be a real pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had always been unsure if I\Nwanted to stay here forever or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, once I saw them,\NI finally made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that, as a man, I must\Nset out onto the vast ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm leaving this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's but one reason:\Nthe pirate flag is calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! You're lying, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying again, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's way too hasty to do that!\NDon't you love this village, Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to the Usopp Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been great to me, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to leave without telling\Nthe villagers. Give them my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No...\N--I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:12:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All done!\N--Liar guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you guys?!\NDon't treat me all buddy-like!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're a famous person...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, people've finally started to\Nrespectfully call me Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone calls you Liar Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! From this day forth,\Nyou're members of the Usopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot's happened, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Cerberus! Scare it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon! Capture it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flour Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!\NI am a brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wanna hear\Nabout the old days!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We don't wanna hear about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you, Captain!\NWhy are you saying this stuff now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stupid, Captain! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are your ambitions in life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To run a pub!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be a master carpenter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be a novel writer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then swear here that you'll\Ncontinue on each of your paths
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and never let the fires\Nof your ambitions go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of today...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Usopp Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are disbanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Food"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've eaten.\NWe should get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here you are!\N--Hey, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, being out of bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sickness this past year
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was caused by the mental dismay\Nfrom having lost my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Usopp-san really\Ncheered me up, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay coddled forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done so much for me. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared a present for you\Nfrom the bottom of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All packed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's farewell to this house, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...? I can't get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A caravel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really have this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a slightly older model,\Nbut I personally designed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A carvel-make caravel, with lateen\Nsails and a central stern rudder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain the running rigging!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, about the Kruger\Nnet yard adjustment--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! You can explain\Nthe ship stuff to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good ship! Especially\Nthis front-- it's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've loaded it with everything\Nyou might need on a voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! It leaves nothing to beat tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's "leaves nothing\Nto be desired," you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just stop him for now.\NHe's on a collision course with the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are taking to\Nthe ocean, Usopp-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've decided to get going\Nbefore I start to change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop me, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't. I could just tell somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of sad, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time I come to this village,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you adventure stories that\Nseem even more lie-like than lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys take care, too!\NLet's meet again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How come?\N--Huh? "How come?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're antisocial...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:18:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be a pirate too, so we'll\Nmeet on the high seas eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talkin' about?\NGet on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to be captain, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be dumb! I'm the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There goes the captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But he's with those guys,\Nso I feel less worried now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've never seen anyone\Nas strong as them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always talked about\Nhow he wanted to be a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The villagers'll probably be\Nsad when we tell them, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all so sudden, plus he\Nlivened things up all by himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is it?!\N--What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were certainly pleasant people...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Merry...\N--Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lying hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you referring to Klahadore?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean how you really wanted\Nto stop Usopp-kun from going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, the villagers once told\Nme a story from his childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shortly after Usopp-kun's\Nfather left the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his mother passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's pirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on, Usopp!\NYou mustn't shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad came back for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be silly... Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said he'd take us with\Nhim when you get better, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father won't be coming back...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm proud I married him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There's a legendary medicine!\NIt can cure any sickness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so silly... You dream too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if I'm silly!\NI do dream! I am the son of a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grow up to be a brave\Nman like your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps out of his loneliness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he continued to shout it out\Nafter his mother's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the hopes that one day his father's\Npirate ship would be at the shore,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the hopes that one day\Nhe would come back for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The villagers say that lie\Nof his also contains his wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As someone who lost his\Nown parents in this village,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he probably couldn't ignore you,\Nseeing as the same happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will need to grow\Nstronger now, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To live up to everything\Nhe's done until today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers to our new ship and crewmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they were\Nfighting to live, not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san's lies always\Nspoke about the joy of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They cheered me up\Nand told me to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really gonna do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet! We're following\Nin our captain's footsteps!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ready...\N--Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.61,0:22:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Pirates are here!\N--Pirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what, Merry?\NI'm going to be a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a wonderful goal to have!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.62,0:24:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This island gives me\Nthe creeps! Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.14,0:24:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure-hunting, huh?!\NThat sounds exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.71,0:24:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! There's something here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?!\NHe's totally suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Says he's the protective\Ngod of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.39,0:24:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neat! A scrub brush!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.99,0:24:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.42,0:24:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're the Weird Creature!\NGaimon and His Strange Friends"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.73,0:24:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
